<doc id="1179579" wikidata="Q4655965" url="?curid=1179579" title="A Clearing in the Distance">
<text>A Clearing in the Distance: Frederick Law Olmsted and North America in the Nineteenth Century is a biography of 19th-century landscape architect Frederick Law Olmsted, published in 1999, by Canadian architect, professor and writer Witold Rybczynski.

It was short-listed for the Charles Taylor Prize in 2000.

